00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:10.960
<v Speaker 1>The four options of lo, la, los, las.

00:00:10.639 --> 00:00:15.760
<v Speaker 1>become less and less when it's to him, to her, for him, for her.

00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:20.560
<v Speaker 1>And we said that me, te and nos they don't change to get these different meanings.

00:00:20.140 --> 00:00:21.420
<v Speaker 1>They stay as they are.

00:00:21.420 --> 00:00:30.779
<v Speaker 1>And we also saw that these words medte and nos can mean myself, yourself, ourselves or each other.

